<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>무안경찰서 범죄예방가이드</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css?v=10">
  <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials_header', { isAdmin: isAdmin }) %>
<div class="top-quick">
  <a href="/practice-112" class="quick-112">🚨 112 신고연습</a>
</div>
  <div class="home-shell">
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-top">
        <div class="hero-badge">
          <img src="/police_logo.png" alt="경찰 로고" class="hero-logo">
        </div>

        <div class="hero-title-wrap">
          <div class="hero-sub">Crime Prevention Guide</div>
          <h1 class="hero-title">무안경찰서<br>범죄예방 가이드</h1>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-line"></div>

      <p class="hero-desc">
        주민 안전을 위한 범죄예방 정보를 제공합니다.
      </p>

      <% if (isAdmin && adminName) { %>
        <div class="hero-admin">
          관리자 로그인: <strong><%= adminName %></strong>
        </div>
      <% } %>
    </section>

    <section class="category-grid">
      <% categories.forEach(category => { %>
        <a href="/category/<%= category.key %>" class="category-card card-<%= category.key %>">
          <div class="category-icon-wrap">
            <span class="category-icon"><%= category.icon %></span>
          </div>

          <div class="category-title"><%= category.name %></div>

          <div class="category-desc">
            <% if (category.key === 'theft') { %>
              절도 예방 수칙 안내
            <% } else if (category.key === 'fraud') { %>
              피싱, 사기 수법 안내
            <% } else if (category.key === 'foreign') { %>
              외국인 대상 범죄예방수칙 안내
            <% } else if (category.key === 'notice') { %>
              공지사항 및 소식
            <% } else { %>
              무안경찰 알림
            <% } %>
          </div>
        </a>
      <% }) %>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
